title: 216 - Incoming Top Gun Nick
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off with a FULL BARN as they dive into the latest updates, as the lad of the lads, Gumpy is on his Canadian voyage. The boys then jump right into the Pod FOD which is a folder compiled of all things around the internet. Todays FOD includes a Nicky Skates break DAHN of Top Gun 2, Connor’s fear of Stranger things season 4, a Sharkcano, and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
